OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA fine day, with plenty of
OL,6,Fsunshine and temperatures increasing
OL,7,Fagain. Brisk southeasterly winds
OL,8,Fexpected, with some strong gusts along
OL,9,Fthe coast. Isolated showers possible
OL,10,Fin the afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry but
OL,13,Fa little cooler on Friday. A band of
OL,14,Fpatchy rain moving in late on
OL,15,FSaturday, perhaps heavy and persistent
OL,16,Fovernight. Unsettled with showers
OL,17,Fpossible on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
